{"id":2595,"date":"2025-05-13T15:57:25","date_gmt":"2025-05-13T08:57:25","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=2595"},"modified":"2025-05-15T14:36:58","modified_gmt":"2025-05-15T07:36:58","slug":"mat-na-nang-co-mat","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/xu-huong\/mat-na-nang-co-mat\/","title":{"rendered":"M\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 m\u1eb7t \u2013 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng, n\u00e2ng c\u01a1"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><i>M\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 m\u1eb7t<\/i><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u2013 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p gi\u00fap da s\u0103n ch\u1eafc, c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng, ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba ch\u1ea3y x\u1ec7 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn spa hay can thi\u1ec7p th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang lo l\u1eafng v\u00ec l\u00e0n da m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i, xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n v\u00e0 k\u00e9m t\u01b0\u01a1i t\u1eafn, b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 t\u1ea1i sao <\/span><\/i><b><i>m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 m\u1eb7t H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c<\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1i \u01b0u. GSC \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch, \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"mat-na-mang-lai-tac-dung-gi\"><\/span><b>M\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 mang l\u1ea1i t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng g\u00ec?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch, m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da gi\u00fap h\u1ea5p n\u00e2ng c\u01a1, c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 tr\u1ebb ho\u00e1 da. Ngo\u00e0i ra, vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1eafp m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 c\u00f2n mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh spa ngay t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0, gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1eebng lo\u1ea1i m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 s\u1ebd d\u00e0nh cho t\u1eebng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 da ho\u1eb7c mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng. Hi\u1ec7n nay, th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng cung c\u1ea5p \u0111a d\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng chuy\u00ean bi\u1ec7t cho t\u1eebng nhu c\u1ea7u da kh\u00e1c nhau, ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn bao g\u1ed3m:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2596\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2596\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2596 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/cac-loai-mat-na-nang-co-mat.webp\" alt=\"M\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 mang l\u1ea1i t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng g\u00ec?\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/cac-loai-mat-na-nang-co-mat.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/cac-loai-mat-na-nang-co-mat-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/cac-loai-mat-na-nang-co-mat-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/cac-loai-mat-na-nang-co-mat-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2596\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>M\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 mang l\u1ea1i t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng g\u00ec<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mask gi\u1ea5y<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mask b\u1ed9t<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mask kem<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mask \u0111\u1ea5t s\u00e9t<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mask gel<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">D\u00f9 m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap da c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng, nh\u01b0ng t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng mang t\u00ednh t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi. \u0110\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh l\u00e2u d\u00e0i, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u. C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia khuy\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb n\u00ean \u0111\u1eafp m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 t\u1eeb 1-3 l\u1ea7n m\u1ed7i tu\u1ea7n, t\u00f9y theo nhu c\u1ea7u v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i da.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ai-thuc-su-can-su-dung-mat-na-nang-co\"><\/span><b>Ai th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eeb 25 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf l\u00ean, khi l\u00e0n da b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u l\u00e3o h\u00f3a \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da ch\u1ea3y x\u1ec7 s\u1edbm do c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, thi\u1ebfu ng\u1ee7 ho\u1eb7c t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec l\u00e0n da s\u0103n ch\u1eafc.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2599\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2599\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2599 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/mat-na-nang-co-mat-tot.webp\" alt=\"Ai th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/mat-na-nang-co-mat-tot.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/mat-na-nang-co-mat-tot-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/mat-na-nang-co-mat-tot-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/mat-na-nang-co-mat-tot-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2599\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Ai th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y l\u00e0n da c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 k\u0129 c\u00e0ng h\u01a1n:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Da b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u1ea3y x\u1ec7, thi\u1ebfu s\u0103n ch\u1eafc.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf r\u00e3nh c\u01b0\u1eddi, kh\u00f3e m\u1eaft.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Da x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u, m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i, s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c da m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i, d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u v\u1ebft khi nh\u1ea5n v\u00e0o.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"so-sanh-mat-na-nang-co-va-cac-phuong-phap-khac-%e2%80%93-dau-la-lua-chon-toi-uu\"><\/span><b>So s\u00e1nh m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p kh\u00e1c \u2013 \u0110\u00e2u l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1i \u01b0u?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u00e2u d\u00e0i, l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh an to\u00e0n<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">D\u1ea1ng gel n\u00ean n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb d\u00ednh<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u00e1y massage<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">K\u00edch th\u00edch tu\u1ea7n ho\u00e0n m\u00e1u, th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n da<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1eaft ti\u1ec1n, y\u00eau c\u1ea7u k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng, n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 t\u1ee9c th\u00ec<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chi ph\u00ed cao, c\u00f3 r\u1ee7i ro<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng n\u00e2ng c\u01a1<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i, d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 ch\u1eadm, kh\u00f4ng n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 t\u1ee9c th\u00ec<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"gsc-mat-na-nang-co-%e2%80%93-bi-quyet-giup-da-cang-bong-nang-co-toan-dien\"><\/span><b>GSC M\u1eb7t N\u1ea1 N\u00e2ng C\u01a1 \u2013 B\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap da c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng, n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"vi-sao-moi-nguoi-tin-dung-mat-na-nang-co-mat-gsc\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u00ec sao m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi tin d\u00f9ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 m\u1eb7t GSC?<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c chuy\u00ean bi\u1ec7t: K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t <\/span><b>m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m, gi\u00fap da v\u1eeba s\u0103n ch\u1eafc v\u1eeba m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">D\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u: Ch\u1ee9a collagen th\u1ee7y ph\u00e2n, peptide v\u00e0 nano v\u00e0ng gi\u00fap t\u0103ng sinh collagen t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 th\u1eadt: Da c\u0103ng m\u01b0\u1edbt, b\u00f3ng m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng ngay l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 t\u1ee9c th\u00ec.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">An to\u00e0n, l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh: Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i cho da.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cach-mat-na-nang-co-mat-tac-dong-den-lan-da\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e1ch m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 m\u1eb7t t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0n da\u00a0<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc cung c\u1ea5p d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t s\u00e2u v\u00e0o da, gi\u00fap:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t collagen v\u00e0 elastin t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9 s\u0103n ch\u1eafc v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i c\u1ee7a l\u00e0n da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Thanh l\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ed9c t\u1ed1, th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y tu\u1ea7n ho\u00e0n m\u00e1u, gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng, r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1 v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe kho\u1eafn h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i, n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 t\u1ee9c th\u00ec, gi\u00fap khu\u00f4n m\u1eb7t tr\u1edf n\u00ean thon g\u1ecdn v\u00e0 tr\u1ebb trung h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">S\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t sinh h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn gi\u00fap da h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u da ch\u1ec9 sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-nghe-dot-pha-thanh-phan-vang-trong-mat-na-nang-co-mat\"><\/span><b>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 &amp; Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n v\u00e0ng trong m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 m\u1eb7t<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-nghe-tien-tien-%e2%80%93-chia-khoa-giup-da-san-chac-dan-hoi\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn \u2013 Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a gi\u00fap da s\u0103n ch\u1eafc, \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2598\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2598\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2598 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/mat-na-nang-co-mat-gsc.webp\" alt=\"C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn \u2013 Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a gi\u00fap da s\u0103n ch\u1eafc, \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/mat-na-nang-co-mat-gsc.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/mat-na-nang-co-mat-gsc-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/mat-na-nang-co-mat-gsc-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/mat-na-nang-co-mat-gsc-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2598\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>M\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 m\u1eb7t GSC \u2013 Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a gi\u00fap da s\u0103n ch\u1eafc, \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 Peptide ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn: Khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch da t\u1ef1 t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p collagen, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9 s\u0103n ch\u1eafc r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Collagen th\u1ee7y ph\u00e2n v\u1edbi c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac si\u00eau nh\u1ecf: Th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u nhanh ch\u00f3ng, b\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nano v\u00e0ng 24K: Th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c t\u1ed1, th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o, l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"thanh-phan-noi-bat-%e2%80%93-dinh-duong-chuyen-sau-cho-lan-da-tuoi-tre\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u2013 Dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u cho l\u00e0n da t\u01b0\u01a1i tr\u1ebb<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Collagen th\u1ee7y ph\u00e2n, 6 chu\u1ed7i peptide, amino acid: H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1, t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t d\u1ea7u jojoba, hoa anh th\u1ea3o, macca, hoa t\u1ea7m xu\u00e2n: D\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m, gi\u00fap da c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tripeptide-1, Palmitoyl Tripeptide-1 v\u00e0 chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t rau m\u00e1: B\u1ed9 ba ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0ng gi\u00fap t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"huong-dan-su-dung-mat-na-nang-co-gsc-dat-ket-qua-tot-nhat\"><\/span><b>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 GSC \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2600\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2600\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2600 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/routine-mat-na-nang-co-mat.webp\" alt=\"H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 GSC \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/routine-mat-na-nang-co-mat.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/routine-mat-na-nang-co-mat-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/routine-mat-na-nang-co-mat-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/routine-mat-na-nang-co-mat-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2600\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 m\u1eb7t GSC \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da th\u1eadt k\u1ef9 v\u1edbi lo\u1ea1i s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba v\u00e0 t\u1ea1p ch\u1ea5t t\u00edch t\u1ee5 tr\u00ean da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng toner d\u1ea1ng x\u1ecbt \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 pH tr\u00ean da, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 da h\u1ea5p thu t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfp theo.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: Thoa m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eafp khu\u00f4n m\u1eb7t, tr\u00e1nh v\u00f9ng da m\u1ecfng quanh m\u1eaft v\u00e0 m\u00f4i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: Gi\u1eef m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 tr\u00ean da t\u1eeb 20-30 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o c\u00e1c tinh ch\u1ea5t th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u s\u00e2u v\u00e0o da, \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ebfn khi m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 kh\u00f4 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 5: Nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng th\u00e1o m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 ra kh\u1ecfi da, sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u1ed7 nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng gi\u00fap d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u s\u00e2u h\u01a1n m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n r\u1eeda l\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 6: Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da theo quy tr\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Da l\u00e3o h\u00f3a n\u1eb7ng: 2-3 l\u1ea7n\/tu\u1ea7n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Da l\u00e3o h\u00f3a nh\u1eb9: 1-2 l\u1ea7n\/tu\u1ea7n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 <a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/\"><strong>GSC<\/strong> <\/a>l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p an to\u00e0n, ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n duy tr\u00ec l\u00e0n da tr\u1ebb trung, s\u0103n ch\u1eafc. So v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 kh\u00e1c, <\/span><b>m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 m\u1eb7t <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i m\u00e0 c\u00f2n cung c\u1ea5p d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft y\u1ebfu cho da. S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n nhanh ch\u00f3ng c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t tr\u00ean l\u00e0n da.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>M\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 m\u1eb7t \u2013 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p gi\u00fap da s\u0103n ch\u1eafc, c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng, ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba ch\u1ea3y x\u1ec7 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn spa hay can thi\u1ec7p th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":2597,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[13],"tags":[8,55],"class_list":["post-2595","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-xu-huong","tag-new","tag-san-pham-gsc"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2595","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2595"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2595\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3029,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2595\/revisions\/3029"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2597"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2595"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2595"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2595"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}